𝗔𝗯𝗼𝘂𝘁 𝗺𝗲:
Being raised bilingual (Dutch and Portuguese) in the multi-cultural city of Rotterdam, I developed an interest in people and communication from an early age. 🌍

I fell in love with the world of digital marketing and technology while completing a digital marketing internship in Paris (back in 2013). From then on my pursuit in the field of marketing took me to São Paulo, Valencia, Amsterdam, Tilburg, and Rotterdam.📱

𝗦𝘂𝗺𝗺𝗮𝗿𝘆:
•	7 years of experience in digital marketing (SEO, SEA, social advertising, email, CRO);
•	6 years of experience at digital agencies;
•	I use data-driven insights to develop effective marketing tactics;
•	I speak 5 languages (🇳🇱🇵🇹🇬🇧🇪🇸🇫🇷);
•	Currently in the process of learning Italian. 🇮🇹

𝗣𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆:
Team player, optimist, eager to learn, motivated, analytical, ambitious, results-driven, strong communicator, stress-resistant, easily switch from serious to play (and vice versa), multilingual.

𝗠𝘆 𝘄𝗼𝗿𝗸 𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗼𝘀:
